---

<!-- Bold CTA section with section-bg-success.jpg background -->
<section class="relative overflow-hidden py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-28" data-aos="fade-up">
  <!-- Background image -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <img
      src="/images/generated/section-bg-success.jpg"
      alt=""
      width="1024" height="1024"
      decoding="async"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
      loading="lazy"
      aria-hidden="true"
    />
    <!-- Navy overlay for contrast -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-accent-900/70"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">

      <!-- Urgency indicator -->
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary-400/20 border border-primary-400/40 rounded-full px-4 py-2 mb-8">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary-400 animate-pulse"></span>
        <span class="text-primary-300 font-body font-medium text-sm">Currently accepting new clients</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Headline -->
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-white" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.1;">
        Ready to Transform Your Success?
      </h2>

      <!-- Subtext -->
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-accent-100 font-body leading-relaxed">
        My proven 5-step approach guides you to discover your true vision, grow your self-awareness, use your insightfulness, develop your plan, and take sustainable action. Start with a free Energy Leadership Strategy Session — no pressure, just clarity.
      </p>

      <!-- CTA Buttons -->
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-primary-400 hover:bg-primary-300 text-accent-900 font-body font-semibold rounded-xl text-base transition-colors shadow-lg"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
          Book Your Free Session
        </a>
        <a
          href="/services"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white/60 hover:border-white text-white font-body font-medium rounded-xl text-base transition-colors"
        >
          Explore Services
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Reassurance note -->
      <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-accent-300 font-body">
        Your first session is completely free — 30 to 60 minutes focused on clarity, awareness, and your next-level strategy.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
